modName: Age of Conan - Main Theme Replacer
summary: This mod simply replaces the main menu theme with The Dreaming - Ere the World Crumbles from the Age of Conan soundtrack.
descriptionHtml:
This mod simply replaces the main menu theme with The Dreaming - Ere the World Crumbles from the Age of Conan soundtrack. If you are not familiar with the track, give the link below a listen.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Kn99vRCbww

Disclaimer: I didn\'t create the song, I don\'t own it, I\'m not selling it, yadda yadda.
author: Auddi
